    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable and stylish ride? This well-maintained vehicle is in good condition and ready for its next adventure! It offers a smooth driving experience, a clean interior, and has been cared for to ensure it stays dependable for years to come. It's the perfect blend of quality and value for anyone seeking a solid, road-ready car.",
