      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor door dings, and fading in the clear coat on the roof and hood. Inside, the cabin is clean but displays clear signs of use, including some wear on the driver's seat bolster and minor staining on the carpet. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may eventually need routine maintenance items like new brake pads or tires. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has been used regularly and is priced to reflect its current state.",
      "price": 19000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in pristine condition, this vehicle stands as a testament to meticulous stewardship and automotive excellence. Its exterior and interior surfaces remain in an exemplary state, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is an authoritative acquisition for those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
